#
#   INVENTAR v0.14.0
#
#   KLASSEN (43):
#     Object (7), Data (11), Agent (5), Process (1), Boundary (1),
#     Lex (1), Structura (1), Possibile (1), Norma (4),
#     Institutio (4), Typus (7)
#
#   FASSADEN (40):  35 OP + 5 DP  (owl:equivalentProperty → MIN)
#   EIGENE OP (24): v0.12.0 (10), v0.13.0 (5), v0.13.1 (6), v0.14.0 (3)
#   EIGENE DP (19): v0.12.0 (7), v0.13.0 (5), v0.13.1 (4), v0.14.0 (3)
#   DISJUNKTHEITSAXIOME (5): Object, Agent, Norma, Institutio, Typus
#   MODELING PATTERNS (15): rein sdata:
#
